<p>Janrain Engage is a service that makes it easy for users to sign in or register on your site using an existing account from Google, Yahoo, AOL, Facebook, MySpace, Twitter and others without having to use a new password. By reducing the barriers for users, it can increase site registration and participation. For more information visit the <a href="http://www.janrain.com/products/engage">Janrain Engage</a> site.</p>
<p>If you already have a Janrain Engage account for this site, you should enter the API key and then click the Setup Janrain Engage button.</p>
<p>If you don't yet have an account, leave all fields blank and click the Setup Janrain Engage button. You will be redirected to the Janrain Engage site and after completing the account setup, they will redirect you back here and the settings will be updated automatically.</p>
